{"tid":1382470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家都好累，好負面，不如一齊清下壞情緒","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T13:34:42.000Z","uid":68263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0e34deb87a335d533a8f1ba341923655b70fb79f","tid":1382470,"uid":68263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:11:46.000Z","msg":"無宗教信仰，不過有時聽下頌砵個人可以平靜到落黎。<br />\n<br />\n無能為力嘅感覺由反國教、高鐵菜園到佔中到今日，無時無刻都圍繞住我。我仍然會氣餒，時不時都想做個藍絲港豬，得閒就指住TVB入面啲暴徒恥笑。不過我知我過唔到自己嗰關，亦永遠不能習慣麻木。<br />\n<br />\n所以，請疲累嘅你，用自己嘅方法去排走無力感、失落悲哀痛苦，同我分享你嘅方法。<br />\n<br />\n我地一齊再繼續行落去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XHcMhqK9XPY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXHcMhqK9XPY&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=e6eb4d3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XHcMhqK9XPY</a>"},{"pid":"878b18861597ef6a86818a59f185122e6676f2f5","tid":1382470,"uid":68263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:13:08.000Z","msg":"識有個朋友會不停彈scale幾個鐘<br />\n彈到攰為止"},{"pid":"2f117cf3fbc417998bd424cb96e91f9672e4220e","tid":1382470,"uid":68263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19ff09d5c4514f9279df1ca201cb447894a284b","tid":1382470,"uid":68263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"體能要練勁啲<br />\n心臟都要變強<br />\n精神力神都要變強！"},{"pid":"f171c8a0ca2b1a36f240013807444fbeb6af7662","tid":1382470,"uid":11937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:20:15.000Z","msg":"互相推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「全港大罷工」動搖唔到經濟民生佔晒全香港都無用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsovuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsovuS</a>"},{"pid":"7c0b0d9e99e9a2fae6ec5b24b25c0bceb826f7c1","tid":1382470,"uid":68263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07